#: ../../docs/user_manual/introduction/getting_started.rst:8
msgid "Getting Started"
msgstr "Početak"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/introduction/getting_started.rst:15
msgid ""
"This chapter provides a quick overview of installing QGIS, downloading QGIS "
"sample data, and running a first simple session visualizing raster and "
"vector data."
msgstr ""
"Ovo poglavlje pruža kratak pregled instaliranja QGIS-a, preuzimanja QGIS "
"primernih podataka i pokretanja prve jednostavne sesije vizuelizacije "
"rasterskih i vektorskih podataka."

#: ../../docs/user_manual/introduction/getting_started.rst:23
msgid "Installing QGIS"
msgstr "Instaliranje QGIS-a"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/introduction/getting_started.rst:25
msgid ""
"QGIS project provides different ways to install QGIS depending on your "
"platform."
msgstr ""
"QGIS projekat pruža različite načine za instaliranje QGIS-a u zavisnosti od "
"vaše platforme."

#: ../../docs/user_manual/introduction/getting_started.rst:28
msgid "Installing from binaries"
msgstr "Instaliranje iz binarnih datoteka"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/introduction/getting_started.rst:30
msgid ""
"Standard installers are available for |win| MS Windows and |osx| macOS. "
"Binary packages (rpm and deb) or software repositories are provided for many"
" flavors of GNU/Linux |nix|."
msgstr ""
"Standardni instalateri su dostupni za |win| MS Windows i |osx| macOS. "
"Binarni paketi (rpm i deb) ili softverski repozitorijumi su obezbeđjeni za "
"mnoge varijante GNU/Linux |nix|."

#: ../../docs/user_manual/introduction/getting_started.rst:330
msgid "win"
msgstr "win"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/introduction/getting_started.rst:316
msgid "osx"
msgstr "osx"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/introduction/getting_started.rst:314
msgid "nix"
msgstr "nix"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/introduction/getting_started.rst:34
msgid ""
"For more information and instructions for your operating system check "
"https://qgis.org/download/."
msgstr ""
"Za više informacija i uputstava za vaš operativni sistem posetite "
"https://qgis.org/download/."

#: ../../docs/user_manual/introduction/getting_started.rst:38
msgid "Installing from source"
msgstr "Instaliranje iz izvornog koda"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/introduction/getting_started.rst:40
msgid ""
"If you need to build QGIS from source, please refer to the installation "
"instructions. They are distributed with the QGIS source code in a file "
"called :file:`INSTALL`. You can also find them online at "
":source:`INSTALL.md`."
msgstr ""
"Ako treba da napravite QGIS iz izvornog koda, pogledajte uputstva za "
"instalaciju. Ona se distribuiraju sa izvornim kodom QGIS-a u datoteci pod "
"nazivom :file:`INSTALL`. Takodje ih možete pronaći na mreži na "
":source:`INSTALL.md`."

#: ../../docs/user_manual/introduction/getting_started.rst:45
msgid ""
"If you want to build a particular release and not the version in "
"development, you should replace ``master`` with the release branch (commonly"
" in the ``release-X_Y`` form) in the above-mentioned link (installation "
"instructions may differ)."
msgstr ""
"Ako želite da napravite određjeno izdanje, a ne verziju u razvoju, trebalo "
"bi da zamenite ``master`` sa granom release (obično u obliku ``release-"
"X_Y``) u gore pomenutom linku (uputstva za instalaciju mogu se razlikovati)."

#: ../../docs/user_manual/introduction/getting_started.rst:50
msgid "Installing on external media"
msgstr "Instaliranje na eksterne medije"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/introduction/getting_started.rst:52
msgid ""
"It is possible to install QGIS (with all plugins and settings) on a flash "
"drive. This is achieved by defining a :ref:`--profiles-path <profiles-"
"path_option>` option that overrides the default :ref:`user profile "
"<user_profiles>` path and forces **QSettings** to use this directory, too. "
"See section :ref:`env_options` for additional information."
msgstr ""
"Moguće je instalirati QGIS (sa svim dodacima i podešavanjima) na fleš\n"
"disk. To se postiže definisanjem opcije :ref:`--profiles-path\n"
"<profiles-path_option>` koja zamenjuje podrazumevanu putanju\n"
":ref:`korisnički profil <user_profiles>` i primorava **QSettings** da\n"
"takođe koristi ovaj direktorijum. Pogledajte odeljak :ref:`env_options`\n"
"za dodatne informacije."

#: ../../docs/user_manual/introduction/getting_started.rst:66
msgid "Downloading sample data"
msgstr "Preuzimanje primernih podataka"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/introduction/getting_started.rst:68
msgid ""
"This user guide contains examples based on the QGIS sample dataset (also "
"called the ``Alaska dataset``).  Download the sample data from "
"https://github.com/qgis/QGIS-Sample-Data/archive/master.zip and unzip the "
"archive on any convenient location on your system."
msgstr ""
"Ovaj korisnički vodič sadrži primere zasnovane na QGIS uzorku skupa podataka"
" (takođje nazvanom „Aljaski skup podataka“). Preuzmite uzorke podataka sa "
"https://github.com/qgis/QGIS-Sample-Data/archive/master.zip i raspakujte "
"arhivu na bilo koju pogodnu lokaciju na vašem sistemu."

#: ../../docs/user_manual/introduction/getting_started.rst:73
msgid ""
"The Alaska dataset includes all GIS data that are used for the examples and "
"screenshots in this user guide; it also includes a small GRASS database. The"
" projection for the QGIS sample datasets is Alaska Albers Equal Area with "
"units feet. The EPSG code is 2964."
msgstr ""
"Skup podataka za Aljasku sadrži sve GIS podatke koji se koriste za primere i"
" snimke ekrana u ovom korisničkom vodiču; takođje uključuje malu GRASS bazu "
"podataka. Projekcija za QGIS primere skupova podataka je Aljaska Albers "
"jednaka površina sa jedinicama stopa. EPSG kod je 2964."

#: ../../docs/user_manual/introduction/getting_started.rst:101
msgid ""
"If you intend to use QGIS as a graphical front end for GRASS, you can find a"
" selection of sample locations (e.g., Spearfish or South Dakota) at the "
"official GRASS GIS website, https://grass.osgeo.org/download/data/."
msgstr ""
"Ako nameravate da koristite QGIS kao grafički interfejs za GRASS, možete "
"pronaći izbor primera lokacija (npr. Spearfish ili Južna Dakota) na "
"zvaničnoj GRASS GIS veb stranici, https://grass.osgeo.org/download/data/."

#: ../../docs/user_manual/introduction/getting_started.rst:109
msgid "Starting and stopping QGIS"
msgstr "Pokretanje i zaustavljanje QGIS-a"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/introduction/getting_started.rst:111
msgid ""
"QGIS can be started like any other application on your computer. This means "
"that you can launch QGIS by:"
msgstr ""
"QGIS se može pokrenuti kao i bilo koja druga aplikacija na vašem računaru. "
"To znači da QGIS možete pokrenuti na sledeći način:"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/introduction/getting_started.rst:114
msgid ""
"using |nix| the Applications menu, |win| the Start menu, or |osx| the Dock"
msgstr ""
"korišćenjem |nix| menija Aplikacije, |win| menija Start ili |osx| Dock-a"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/introduction/getting_started.rst:115
msgid ""
"double clicking the icon in your Applications folder or desktop shortcut"
msgstr ""
"dvostrukim klikom na ikonu u folderu Aplikacije ili prečici na radnoj "
"površini"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/introduction/getting_started.rst:116
msgid ""
"double clicking an existing QGIS project file (with :file:`.qgz` or "
":file:`.qgs` extension). Note that this will also open the project."
msgstr ""
"dvostrukim klikom na postojeću datoteku QGIS projekta (sa ekstenzijom "
":file:`.qgz` ili :file:`.qgs`). Imajte na umu da će se ovim takođe otvoriti"
" projekat."

#: ../../docs/user_manual/introduction/getting_started.rst:118
msgid ""
"typing ``qgis`` in a command prompt (assuming that QGIS is added to your "
"PATH or you are in its installation folder)"
msgstr ""
"kucanjem „qgis“ u komandnoj liniji (pod pretpostavkom da je QGIS dodat u "
"vašu putanju ili da ste u njegovoj instalacionoj fascikli)"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/introduction/getting_started.rst:121
msgid "To stop QGIS, use:"
msgstr "Da biste zaustavili QGIS, koristite:"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/introduction/getting_started.rst:123
msgid ""
"|nix| |win| the menu option :menuselection:`Project --> Exit QGIS` or use "
"the shortcut :kbd:`Ctrl+Q`"
msgstr ""
"|nix| |win| opciju menija :menuselection:`Projekat --> Izađji iz QGIS-a` ili"
" koristite prečicu :kbd:`Ctrl+Q`"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/introduction/getting_started.rst:125
msgid ""
"|osx| :menuselection:`QGIS --> Quit QGIS`, or use the shortcut :kbd:`Cmd+Q`"
msgstr ""
"|osx| :menuselection:`QGIS --> Zatvori QGIS`, ili koristi prečicu "
":kbd:`Cmd+Q`"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/introduction/getting_started.rst:126
msgid ""
"or use the red cross at the top-right corner of the main interface of the "
"application."
msgstr ""
"ili koristite crveni krst u gornjem desnom uglu glavnog interfejsa "
"aplikacije."

#: ../../docs/user_manual/introduction/getting_started.rst:132
msgid "Sample Session: Loading raster and vector layers"
msgstr "Primer sesije: Učitavanje rasterskih i vektorskih slojeva"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/introduction/getting_started.rst:134
msgid ""
"Now that you have :ref:`QGIS installed <label_installation>` and a "
":ref:`sample dataset <label_sampledata>` available, we will demonstrate a "
"first sample session. In this example, we will visualize a raster and a "
"vector layer. We will use:"
msgstr ""
"Sada kada imate :ref:`QGIS instaliran <label_installation>` i :ref:`primer "
"skupa podataka <label_sampledata>` dostupan, demonstriraćemo prvu primer "
"sesije. U ovom primeru, vizualizovaćemo rasterski i vektorski sloj. "
"Koristićemo:"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/introduction/getting_started.rst:139
msgid ""
"the :file:`landcover` raster layer "
"(:file:`qgis_sample_data/raster/landcover.img`)"
msgstr ""
"rasterski sloj :file:`landcover` "
"(:file:`qgis_sample_data/raster/landcover.img`)"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/introduction/getting_started.rst:140
msgid ""
"and the :file:`lakes` vector layer (:file:`qgis_sample_data/gml/lakes.gml`)"
msgstr ""
"i vektorski sloj :file:`lakes` (:file:`qgis_sample_data/gml/lakes.gml`)"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/introduction/getting_started.rst:142
msgid ""
"Where :file:`qgis_sample_data` represents the path to the unzipped dataset."
msgstr ""
"Gde :file:`qgis_sample_data` predstavlja putanju do raspakovanog skupa "
"podataka."

#: ../../docs/user_manual/introduction/getting_started.rst:144
msgid "Start QGIS as seen in :ref:`label_startingqgis`."
msgstr "Pokrenite QGIS kao što je prikazano u :ref:`label_startingqgis`."

#: ../../docs/user_manual/introduction/getting_started.rst:145
msgid ""
"The data we will be working with are in ``Albers Equal Area``, so let's set "
"the project's CRS accordingly:"
msgstr ""
"Podaci sa kojima ćemo raditi su u ``Albers Equal Area``, pa hajde da u "
"skladu sa tim podesimo CRS projekta:"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/introduction/getting_started.rst:148
msgid ""
"Click the |setProjection| :sup:`Select projection` button in the bottom "
"right of QGIS interface. The project properties dialog opens with the "
":guilabel:`CRS` tab active."
msgstr ""
"Kliknite na dugme |setProjection| :sup:`Izbor projekcije` u donjem desnom "
"uglu QGIS interfejsa. Otvara se dijalog svojstava projekta sa aktivnom "
"karticom :guilabel:`CRS`."

#: ../../docs/user_manual/introduction/getting_started.rst:326
msgid "setProjection"
msgstr "setProjection"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/introduction/getting_started.rst:151
msgid "Type ``2964`` in the |search| :guilabel:`Filter` text area."
msgstr "Ukucajte ``2964`` u polje za tekst |search| :guilabel:`Filter`."

#: ../../docs/user_manual/introduction/getting_started.rst:324
msgid "search"
msgstr "search"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/introduction/getting_started.rst:152
msgid "Select the row with ``NAD27 / Alaska Albers`` CRS name."
msgstr "Izaberite red sa nazivom CRS-a ``NAD27 / Alaska Albers``."

#: ../../docs/user_manual/introduction/getting_started.rst:159
msgid "Select the Coordinate Reference System of data"
msgstr "Izbor koordinatnog referentnog sistema podataka"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/introduction/getting_started.rst:161
msgid "Press :guilabel:`OK`"
msgstr "Pritisnite :guilabel:`OK`"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/introduction/getting_started.rst:163
msgid ""
"You can ignore/close for now the \"ballpark transform\" message that could "
"display."
msgstr ""
"Za sada možete ignorisati/zatvoriti poruku „ballpark transform“ koja se može"
" pojaviti."

#: ../../docs/user_manual/introduction/getting_started.rst:166
msgid "Load the files in QGIS:"
msgstr "Učitajte datoteke u QGIS:"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/introduction/getting_started.rst:168
msgid ""
"Click on the |dataSourceManager| :sup:`Open Data Source Manager` icon. The "
"Data Source Manager should open in Browser mode."
msgstr ""
"Kliknite na ikonu |dataSourceManager| :sup:`Otvori upravljač izvorima "
"podataka`. Upravljač izvorima podataka bi trebalo da se otvori u režimu "
"pregledača."

#: ../../docs/user_manual/introduction/getting_started.rst:304
msgid "dataSourceManager"
msgstr "dataSourceManager"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/introduction/getting_started.rst:170
msgid "Browse to the folder :file:`qgis_sample_data/raster/`"
msgstr "Pređite u folder :file:`qgis_sample_data/raster/`"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/introduction/getting_started.rst:171
msgid ""
"Select the ERDAS IMG file |rasterLayer| :guilabel:`landcover.img` and "
"double-click it. The landcover layer is added in the background while the "
"Data Source Manager window remains open."
msgstr ""
"Izaberite ERDAS IMG datoteku |rasterLayer| :guilabel:`landcover.img` i "
"dvaput kliknite na nju. Sloj landcover se dodaje u pozadini dok prozor "
"upravljača izvorima podataka ostaje otvoren."

#: ../../docs/user_manual/introduction/getting_started.rst:320
msgid "rasterLayer"
msgstr "rasterLayer"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/introduction/getting_started.rst:181
msgid "Adding data to a new project in QGIS"
msgstr "Dodavanje podataka u novi projekat u QGIS-u"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/introduction/getting_started.rst:183
msgid ""
"To load the lakes data, browse to the folder :file:`qgis_sample_data/gml/`, "
"and drag and drop the |dbSchema| :guilabel:`lakes.gml` file over QGIS main "
"dialog. (Or just double-click as mentioned above.)"
msgstr ""
"Da biste učitali podatke o jezerima, pređite u folder "
":file:`qgis_sample_data/gml/` i prevucite datoteku |dbSchema| "
":guilabel:`lakes.gml` na glavni prozor QGIS-a. (Ili jednostavno dvaput "
"kliknite kao što je gore pomenuto.)"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/introduction/getting_started.rst:306
msgid "dbSchema"
msgstr "dbSchema"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/introduction/getting_started.rst:186
msgid ""
"The :guilabel:`Select Items to Add` dialog opens, scanning the file. This is"
" due to :file:`.gml` file format being able to store more than one layer at "
"a time."
msgstr ""
"Otvara se dijalog :guilabel:`Izbor stavki za dodavanje` i skenira datoteku. "
"Razlog je to što format datoteke :file:`.gml` može da sadrži više slojeva "
"odjednom."

#: ../../docs/user_manual/introduction/getting_started.rst:194
msgid "Select layers within a file"
msgstr "Izbor slojeva unutar datoteke"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/introduction/getting_started.rst:196
msgid ""
"In our case there is a single |polygonLayer| :guilabel:`lakes` layer. Select"
" it and press :guilabel:`Add Layers`."
msgstr ""
"U našem slučaju postoji samo jedan sloj |polygonLayer| :guilabel:`lakes`. "
"Izaberite ga i pritisnite :guilabel:`Dodaj slojeve`."

#: ../../docs/user_manual/introduction/getting_started.rst:318
msgid "polygonLayer"
msgstr "polygonLayer"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/introduction/getting_started.rst:198
msgid "The layer is added to the :guilabel:`Layers` panel"
msgstr "Sloj se dodaje u panel :guilabel:`Slojevi`"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/introduction/getting_started.rst:199
msgid "Close the Data Source Manager window"
msgstr "Zatvorite prozor upravljača izvorima podataka"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/introduction/getting_started.rst:201
msgid ""
"In the :guilabel:`Layers` panel, you can notice that the :guilabel:`lakes` "
"layer displays |indicatorNoCRS| :sup:`Layer has no coordinate reference "
"system set` next to it. Let's adjust that."
msgstr ""
"U panelu :guilabel:`Slojevi` možete primetiti da sloj :guilabel:`lakes` "
"pored sebe prikazuje |indicatorNoCRS| :sup:`Sloju nije podešen koordinatni "
"referentni sistem`. Hajde da to podesimo."

#: ../../docs/user_manual/introduction/getting_started.rst:310
msgid "indicatorNoCRS"
msgstr "indicatorNoCRS"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/introduction/getting_started.rst:205
msgid ""
"Click the |indicatorNoCRS| icon. The :guilabel:`Coordinate Reference System "
"Selector` dialog opens."
msgstr ""
"Kliknite na ikonu |indicatorNoCRS|. Otvara se dijalog :guilabel:`Izbor "
"koordinatnog referentnog sistema`."

#: ../../docs/user_manual/introduction/getting_started.rst:207
msgid ""
"As done earlier, find and select the :guilabel:`NAD27 / Alaska Albers` CRS "
"entry."
msgstr ""
"Kao i ranije, pronađite i izaberite CRS stavku :guilabel:`NAD27 / Alaska "
"Albers`."

#: ../../docs/user_manual/introduction/getting_started.rst:208
msgid "Click :guilabel:`OK`"
msgstr "Kliknite na :guilabel:`OK`"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/introduction/getting_started.rst:210
msgid ""
"You now have the two layers available in your project in some random "
"colours. Let's do some customization on the lakes layer."
msgstr ""
"Sada imate oba sloja dostupna u projektu, u nasumično dodeljenim bojama. "
"Hajde da malo prilagodimo sloj jezera."

#: ../../docs/user_manual/introduction/getting_started.rst:213
msgid ""
"Select the |zoomIn| :sup:`Zoom In` tool on the :guilabel:`Navigation` "
"toolbar"
msgstr ""
"Izaberite alatku |zoomIn| :sup:`Uvećaj` na traci sa alatkama "
":guilabel:`Navigacija`"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/introduction/getting_started.rst:332
msgid "zoomIn"
msgstr "zoomIn"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/introduction/getting_started.rst:214
msgid "Zoom to an area with some lakes"
msgstr "Uvećajte prikaz na područje sa nekoliko jezera"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/introduction/getting_started.rst:215
msgid ""
"Double-click the :file:`lakes` layer in the map legend to open the "
":guilabel:`Properties` dialog"
msgstr ""
"Dvaput kliknite na sloj :file:`lakes` u legendi karte da biste otvorili "
"dijalog :guilabel:`Svojstva`"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/introduction/getting_started.rst:217
msgid "To change the lakes color:"
msgstr "Da biste promenili boju jezera:"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/introduction/getting_started.rst:219
msgid "Click on the |symbology| :guilabel:`Symbology` tab"
msgstr "Kliknite na karticu |symbology| :guilabel:`Simbologija`"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/introduction/getting_started.rst:328
msgid "symbology"
msgstr "symbology"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/introduction/getting_started.rst:220
msgid "Select blue as fill color."
msgstr "Izaberite plavu kao boju popune."

#: ../../docs/user_manual/introduction/getting_started.rst:227
msgid "Selecting Lakes color"
msgstr "Izbor boje jezera"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/introduction/getting_started.rst:229
msgid ""
"Press :guilabel:`OK`. Lakes are now displayed in blue in the map canvas."
msgstr ""
"Pritisnite :guilabel:`OK`. Jezera se sada prikazuju plavom bojom na platnu "
"karte."

#: ../../docs/user_manual/introduction/getting_started.rst:230
msgid "To display the name of the lakes:"
msgstr "Da biste prikazali nazive jezera:"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/introduction/getting_started.rst:232
msgid "Reopen the :file:`lakes` layer :guilabel:`Properties` dialog"
msgstr "Ponovo otvorite dijalog :guilabel:`Svojstva` sloja :file:`lakes`"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/introduction/getting_started.rst:233
msgid "Click on the |labelingSingle| :guilabel:`Labels` tab"
msgstr "Kliknite na karticu |labelingSingle| :guilabel:`Oznake`"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/introduction/getting_started.rst:312
msgid "labelingSingle"
msgstr "labelingSingle"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/introduction/getting_started.rst:234
msgid ""
"Select :guilabel:`Single labels` in the drop-down menu to enable labeling."
msgstr ""
"Izaberite :guilabel:`Pojedinačne oznake` u padajućem meniju da biste "
"omogućili označavanje."

#: ../../docs/user_manual/introduction/getting_started.rst:235
msgid "From the :guilabel:`Label with` list, choose the ``NAMES`` field."
msgstr "Iz liste :guilabel:`Označi sa` izaberite polje ``NAMES``."

#: ../../docs/user_manual/introduction/getting_started.rst:242
msgid "Showing Lakes names"
msgstr "Prikaz naziva jezera"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/introduction/getting_started.rst:244
msgid "Press :guilabel:`Apply`. Names will now load over the boundaries."
msgstr ""
"Pritisnite :guilabel:`Primeni`. Nazivi će se sada učitati preko granica."

#: ../../docs/user_manual/introduction/getting_started.rst:245
msgid ""
"You can improve readability of the labels by adding a white buffer around "
"them:"
msgstr "Čitljivost oznaka možete poboljšati dodavanjem belog bafera oko njih:"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/introduction/getting_started.rst:247
msgid "Click the :guilabel:`Buffer` tab in the list on the left"
msgstr "Kliknite na karticu :guilabel:`Bafer` u listi sa leve strane"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/introduction/getting_started.rst:248
msgid "Check |checkbox| :guilabel:`Draw text buffer`"
msgstr "Označite |checkbox| :guilabel:`Iscrtaj bafer teksta`"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/introduction/getting_started.rst:302
msgid "checkbox"
msgstr "checkbox"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/introduction/getting_started.rst:249
msgid "Choose ``3`` as buffer size"
msgstr "Izaberite ``3`` kao veličinu bafera"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/introduction/getting_started.rst:250
msgid "Click :guilabel:`Apply`"
msgstr "Kliknite na :guilabel:`Primeni`"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/introduction/getting_started.rst:251
msgid "Check if the result looks good, and update the value if needed."
msgstr ""
"Proverite da li rezultat izgleda dobro i po potrebi izmenite vrednost."

#: ../../docs/user_manual/introduction/getting_started.rst:252
msgid ""
"Finally click :guilabel:`OK` to close the :guilabel:`Layer Properties` "
"dialog and apply the changes."
msgstr ""
"Na kraju kliknite na :guilabel:`OK` da biste zatvorili dijalog "
":guilabel:`Svojstva sloja` i primenili izmene."

#: ../../docs/user_manual/introduction/getting_started.rst:260
msgid "Showing Buffers around Labels"
msgstr "Prikaz bafera oko oznaka"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/introduction/getting_started.rst:262
msgid ""
"Let's now add some decorations in order to shape the map and export it out "
"of QGIS:"
msgstr ""
"Hajde sada da dodamo nekoliko dekoracija kako bismo oblikovali kartu i "
"izvezli je iz QGIS-a:"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/introduction/getting_started.rst:265
msgid "Select :menuselection:`View --> Decorations --> Scale Bar` menu"
msgstr "Izaberite meni :menuselection:`Prikaz --> Dekoracije --> Razmernik`"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/introduction/getting_started.rst:266
msgid ""
"In the dialog that opens, check |checkbox| :guilabel:`Enable Scale Bar` "
"option"
msgstr ""
"U dijalogu koji se otvori označite opciju |checkbox| :guilabel:`Omogući "
"razmernik`"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/introduction/getting_started.rst:267
msgid "Customize the options of the dialog as you want"
msgstr "Prilagodite opcije dijaloga po želji"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/introduction/getting_started.rst:268
msgid "Press :guilabel:`Apply`"
msgstr "Pritisnite :guilabel:`Primeni`"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/introduction/getting_started.rst:269
msgid ""
"Likewise, from the decorations menu, add more items (north arrow, "
"copyright...) to the map canvas with custom properties."
msgstr ""
"Na isti način, iz menija dekoracija, dodajte još stavki (strelica severa, "
"autorska prava...) na platno karte sa prilagođenim svojstvima."

#: ../../docs/user_manual/introduction/getting_started.rst:271
msgid ""
"Click :menuselection:`Project --> Import/Export -->` |saveMapAsImage| "
":menuselection:`Export Map to Image...`"
msgstr ""
"Kliknite na :menuselection:`Projekat --> Uvoz/Izvoz -->` |saveMapAsImage| "
":menuselection:`Izvezi kartu u sliku...`"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/introduction/getting_started.rst:322
msgid "saveMapAsImage"
msgstr "saveMapAsImage"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/introduction/getting_started.rst:273
msgid "Press :guilabel:`Save` in the opened dialog"
msgstr "Pritisnite :guilabel:`Sačuvaj` u dijalogu koji se otvori"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/introduction/getting_started.rst:274
msgid ""
"Select a file location, a format and confirm by pressing :guilabel:`Save` "
"again."
msgstr ""
"Izaberite lokaciju datoteke i format, pa potvrdite ponovnim pritiskom na "
":guilabel:`Sačuvaj`."

#: ../../docs/user_manual/introduction/getting_started.rst:276
msgid ""
"Press :menuselection:`Project -->` |fileSave| :menuselection:`Save...` to "
"store your changes as a :file:`.qgz` project file."
msgstr ""
"Pritisnite :menuselection:`Projekat -->` |fileSave| "
":menuselection:`Sačuvaj...` da biste sačuvali izmene kao :file:`.qgz` "
"datoteku projekta."

#: ../../docs/user_manual/introduction/getting_started.rst:308
msgid "fileSave"
msgstr "fileSave"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/introduction/getting_started.rst:284
msgid "Showing Exported Map with Decorations"
msgstr "Prikaz izvezene karte sa dekoracijama"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/introduction/getting_started.rst:286
msgid ""
"That's it! You can see how easy it is to visualize raster and vector layers "
"in QGIS, configure them and generate your map in an image format you can use"
" in other software. Let's move on to learn more about the available "
"functionality, features and settings, and how to use them."
msgstr ""
"To je to! Vidite koliko je lako vizuelizovati rasterske i vektorske slojeve "
"u QGIS-u, podesiti ih i napraviti kartu u formatu slike koji možete "
"koristiti u drugim programima. Hajde da nastavimo i saznamo više o dostupnim"
" funkcijama, mogućnostima i podešavanjima, i o tome kako se koriste."

#: ../../docs/user_manual/introduction/getting_started.rst:292
msgid ""
"To continue learning QGIS through step-by-step exercises, follow the "
":ref:`Training manual <QGIS-training-manual-index-reference>`."
msgstr ""
"Da biste nastavili da učite QGIS kroz vežbe korak po korak, pratite "
":ref:`Priručnik za obuku <QGIS-training-manual-index-reference>`."
